|]

open XPlot.Plotly

let quarters = 
    quarterlySales
    |> Seq.map(fun item -> item.Quarter)

let salesAmount = 
    quarterlySales
    |> Seq.map(fun item -> item.Amount)

let bar = 
    Bar(
        x = quarters,
        y = salesAmount
    )

bar
|> Chart.Plot
